				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/H%E1%BA%A1-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-Wgt7w2bSjWJuGnqE1f8Ufw">Hạ nhật ngẫu thành kỳ 1 - 夏日偶成其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/L%E1%BA%A1p-nh%E1%BA%ADt-du-C%C3%B4-s%C6%A1n-ph%E1%BB%8Fng-Hu%E1%BB%87-C%E1%BA%A7n-Hu%E1%BB%87-T%C6%B0-nh%E1%BB%8B-t%C4%83ng/poem-GGRnUYQ8KyDAE991NSHYSA">Lạp nhật du Cô sơn phỏng Huệ Cần, Huệ Tư nhị tăng - 臘日遊孤山訪惠勤惠思二僧</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/M%E1%BB%99ng-ti%C3%AAn-th%E1%BA%A5t/poem-EsJFTZTJIrF984MMP55I7A">Mộng tiên thất - 夢先室</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Nam-ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ca-kh%C3%BAc/poem-BI-5R4NCDfEksvoGyyrUTg">Nam phương ca khúc - 南方歌曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/T%E1%BA%B7ng-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Tri%E1%BB%81u-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-ti%C3%AAn-sinh/poem-9qyIE0zAfQUmlmXKzTJufQ">Tặng Đông Triều Phạm tiên sinh - 贈東潮范先生</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/T%E1%BB%A9c-m%E1%BB%A5c/poem-AEH-nxDqoFxOiFAi7pWzOQ">Tức mục - 即目</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C3%BAng/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-GY5JUHoKiRTV2C3cxnzZiA">Xuân nhật tức sự - 春日即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C3%BAng/author-fNknbWPFKAJ0mVTedTVmZA">Nguyễn Thiên Túng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
